IHO S-52 / S-57
---------------

The International Hydrographic Organization (IHO) S-52 and S-57
standards themselves are normative references. This package implements
rendering behaviour specified by those standards. The IHO chart
symbols, lookup tables, and colour tables shipped as compiled assets
in the consuming application (ZedDisplay) derive from the OpenCPN
chartsymbols.xml / rastersymbols-day.png artifacts. OpenCPN's
repository (including data/s57data/) is distributed under GPL-2.0;
there is no LGPL carve-out for the data files. Those assets are data
loaded at runtime, not code linked into this library, and this
package does not redistribute them. The consuming application that
bundles the assets is responsible for honouring GPL-2.0 attribution
and source-availability requirements; see the OpenCPN project at
https://github.com/OpenCPN/OpenCPN for the upstream licence text
(COPYING.gplv2).
